title: Level not registering
body:
so right now on league i'm level 10, but in my boards profile i'm only level 3 how does that work? so now i cant make so discussion i most of the boards.
Help:({{sticker:zombie-nunu-tears}}

replies.body:
Your boards level is actually equal to your Summoner level in the client. You might see a discrepancy at first, but once you post here it should sync your levels. 

Looks like the sync worked, you're showing up as level 10 for me right now ^_^!
